evidence.claim: MediBookr uses AWS services for scalability and storage.
The platform supports FHIR standards for health data interoperability.
MediBookr implements HL7 protocols for healthcare data exchange.
There are mentions of AWS Lambda for serverless integrations within their API documentation.
Integration patterns highlighted include API for EHRs and synchronization with external clearinghouses.

icp.icp_reason: No evidence of X12 transaction handling or clearinghouse services found on their site.
